name: Agog 18 Crazy Scan Tree Mirror
description: @__lindaloh__ 3D sculpture photogrammetry scan of a large tree, revelling in the imperfection of artifacts. One of a collection of 20 individual sculptural pieces from my VR world "Agog", 2021. They are variously luminous, poetic, evocative, shiny, scribbly, wacky, simple, sleek, golden, wonky, clashing, compelling, weird, colourful, minimal, maximal, simple, ethereal...
